OL,17,Fof said: "After prolonged abuse by
OL,18,FPhillip Bowler, his victim bravely
OL,19,Fmade the decision to disclose Bowler's
OL,20,Fabuse, first to a family member and
OL,21,Fthen in turn the Police.
